The dataset for this paper is generated from multiple sources. The timeline of the dataset is from January 2018 to February 2020. 
The data about US tariff towards China and China’s tariff towards US during the US-China trade war is from the website of Peterson Institute for International Economics and the world bank. 
The data about US international trade in goods and services during the trade war period comes from the website of the Bureau of Economic Analysis. 
The US trade in goods with China data is from the website of United States Census Bureau. The monthly GDP and CPI data is referred to YCHARTS’ website. 
And the unemployment rate data comes from the website of Bureau of Labor Statistics.
